1 (h) This section does not do any of the following:
2 (1) Prevent a government employer from disciplining an employee or contractor
3 for ingesting cannabis in the workplace or for working while impaired by
4 cannabis.
5 (2) Apply to the extent that they conflict with a governmental employer's
